# ⛽ Real-Time Cross-Chain Gas Tracker (Ethereum MVP)

A Web3 dashboard built with **Next.js**, **Ethers.js**, and **Zustand**.

This project tracks real-time gas fees on Ethereum using Infura WebSockets and calculates estimated transaction cost in USD using Uniswap V3 ETH/USDC pool data.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Live gas price updates using `WebSocketProvider`
- ✅ ETH/USD price fetched from **Uniswap V3 Swap events**
- ✅ Gas cost estimation in USD
- ✅ Zustand-powered state toggle between "Live" & "Simulation" mode

---

## 🛠️ Stack

- React + Next.js (App Router)
- Ethers.js v6
- Zustand
- Infura RPC & WebSockets
- Uniswap V3 on-chain price data

